title: Purchase a JRNY Pass
body:
Goober DAO suggested to mint a JRNY pass. JRNY Pass will be releasing an additional 2 sets that will also get added to the DAO as a result. This will also make the DAO eligible for future giveaways JRNY does. If our JRNY pass gets selected as a winner in a giveaway, we will vote how to distribute the prizes in a new proposal.

Minting starts today at 11:00PM ET. We also have the option to buy one from secondary market. 

Should the Goober DAO Purchase a JRNY Pass?
author: 0x082a7c12a2ef221A3eEE7c404F9e9d60fAdef97f
